*baselayout-user-1.0.2-r3.ebuild (08 Aug 2006)

  08 Aug 2006; Vincent Strubel <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +baselayout-user-1.0.2-r3.ebuild:
  Change permissions of /tmp to 0700, since it is now only a 
  mount point for tmpfs (see also sys-auth/pam_mount, 
  clip-layout/baselayout-rm).

*baselayout-user-1.0.2-r2.ebuild (27 Jul 2006)

  27 Jul 2006; Vincent Strubel <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +baselayout-user-1.0.2-r2.ebuild:
  Removed device creation, which is now done in the core. See
  clip-layout/rm-devices.
  Also add usr/local to that tree.

*baselayout-user-1.0.2-r1 (22 Jun 2006)

  22 Jun 2006; Vincent Strubel <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +baselayout-user-1.0.2-r1.ebuild:
  Removed BSD ptys, which are no longer supported by clip-kernel.

*baselayout-user-1.0.2 (03 May 2006)

  03 May 2006; Vincent Strubel <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +baselayout-user-1.0.2.ebuild:
  Grrr. vncpasswd should not be in user_root, but in user_priv.
  Move it to baselayout-rm-1.0.2.

